{"time": "2026-04-07 10:23:57.185343+05:30", "level": "DEBUG", "message": "FULL_PAYLOAD [req_62bcd63e8718]: {'model': 'stepfun-ai/step-3.5-flash', 'max_tokens': 8000, 'messages': [{'role': 'user', 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'hi'}], 'reasoning_content': None}], 'system': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'x-anthropic-billing-header: cc_version=2.1.92.a35; cc_entrypoint=cli; cch=d9a8c;'}, {'type': 'text', 'text': \"You are Claude Code, Anthropic's official CLI for Claude.\"}, {'type': 'text', 'text': 'Generate a concise, sentence-case title (3-7 words) that captures the main topic or goal of this coding session. The title should be clear enough that the user recognizes the session in a list. Use sentence case: capitalize only the first word and proper nouns.\\n\\nReturn JSON with a single \"title\" field.\\n\\nGood examples:\\n{\"title\": \"Fix login button on mobile\"}\\n{\"title\": \"Add OAuth authentication\"}\\n{\"title\": \"Debug failing CI tests\"}\\n{\"title\": \"Refactor API client error handling\"}\\n\\nBad (too vague): {\"title\": \"Code changes\"}\\nBad (too long): {\"title\": \"Investigate and fix the issue where the login button does not respond on mobile devices\"}\\nBad (wrong case): {\"title\": \"Fix Login Button On Mobile\"}'}], 'stop_sequences': None, 'stream': True, 'temperature': 1.0, 'top_p': None, 'top_k': None, 'metadata': {'user_id': '{\"device_id\":\"ee75b75f808ea7380a55a936058cc1987067dc043136d30d623c1f9ac605426f\",\"account_uuid\":\"\",\"session_id\":\"2fe0b611-37cf-4069-99a7-ab3f4ac267ef\"}'}, 'tools': [], 'tool_choice': None, 'thinking': None, 'extra_body': None, 'original_model': 'claude-haiku-4-5-20251001', 'resolved_provider_model': 'nvidia_nim/stepfun-ai/step-3.5-flash'}", "module": "api.routes", "function": "create_message", "line": 56}
